title: Symantec.Endpoint.Protection.v12.1.7004.6500.(RU6-MP5)
description:
Symantec Endpoint Protection 12.1.7004.6500 (RU6-MP5)



Symantec Endpoint Protection Full Edition 12.1.7004.6500 (MAC, LINUX, x86/x64)

with Symantec Endpoint Protection Manager for (MAC, LINUX, x86/x64)

Release date: 28 Jun 2016
More information:

What's new:

Adds support for Ubuntu 16.04.
Adds support for a SQL Server 2016 database.
Adds support for VMWare ESX 6.0.
Updates RSA SecurID authentication to support the latest RSA configurations, 
which require a token. This support includes the following:
Continued support of RSA Authentication Agent 6.x.
Added support for RSA Authentication Agent 7.2.x, which allows communication with 
RSA Authentication Manager 8.1 using SID-800 tokens

Note: Un-Managed mode only so dont change from unmanaged client
